      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Jenrick launches 'Protect Programme': the next step in winter rough sleeping plan
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A further £15 million allocated to protect some of the most vulnerable people in our communities.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 5 November 2020
</div>

